{"word":"G576 - ἀποβαίνω - apobaínō - ap-ob-ah'-ee-no - Become","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποβαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apobaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ob-ah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Become</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விட்டிறங்கு, வந்திறங்கு, முடி"},{"paragraph":"to come down from, a ship"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; literally to <i>disembark</i>; figuratively to <i>eventuate:</i> - become, go out, turn.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}